TASKVERIFY=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo run if exists the script ~/agent_test/test2.3.sh. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test2.3.sh. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
